{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events\">Device orientation events <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/DeviceMotionEvent\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>acceleration</code></a></li><li><em><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/interval\"><code>interval</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/rotationRate\"><code>rotationRate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Device Orientation Events 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventAcceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEventAcceleration</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEventRotationRate\"><code>DeviceMotionEventRotationRate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>accelerationIncludingGravity 属性返回设备的加速度的记录，单位为<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meter_per_second_squared\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">米每秒平方（m / s2）</a>。与已移除重力加速度的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code></a>不同，此值是由用户引起的设备的加速度和由重力加速度的总和。</p>\n<p>此值通常不如<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code></a>实用，但是在部分不能自动从加速度数据中移除重力加速度的设备（例如没有陀螺仪的设备），是唯一可用值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">var acceleration = instanceOfDeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity;\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"值","title":"值","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>accelerationIncludingGravity</code>是一个包括三轴（x、y、z）加速度信息的对象，每个轴都有自己的属性：</p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"x\"><code>x</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 x 轴（西到东）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"y\"><code>y</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 y 轴（南到北）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"z\"><code>z</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示 z 轴（下到上）上的加速度</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"说明","id":"说明","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/deviceorientation/#ref-for-dom-devicemotionevent-accelerationincludinggravity④","title":"DeviceOrientation Event Specification"}],"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/accelerationIncludingGravity/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"推荐浏览","title":"推荐浏览","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent/acceleration\"><code>DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">devicemotion (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicemotion_event\"><code>window.ondevicemotion</code></a></li>\n  <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/deviceorientation_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">deviceorientation (en-US)</a></code></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceOrientationEvent\"><code>DeviceOrientationEvent</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Device_orientation_events/Detecting_device_orientation\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Detecting device orientation (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/Orientation_and_motion_data_explained\">Orientation and motion data explained</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"值","id":"值"},{"text":"说明","id":"说明"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"推荐浏览","id":"推荐浏览"}],"summary":"accelerationIncludingGravity 属性返回设备的加速度的记录，单位为米每秒平方（m / s2）。与已移除重力加速度的DeviceMotionEvent.acceleration不同，此值是由用户引起的设备的加速度和由重力加速度的总和。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"DeviceMotionEvent.accelerationIncludingGravity","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent/accelerationincludinggravity","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/devicemotionevent/accelerationincludinggravity/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMotionEvent","title":"DeviceMotionEvent"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DeviceMoti